<a data-tip="p$t$kaiserwang730" href="/people/kaiserwang730">Kaiser</a>，<strong title="天亮了" class="zu-question-my-bio">天亮了</strong>

</h3>
<a href="javascript:;" name="collapse" class="collapse meta-item zg-right"><i class="z-icon-fold"></i>收起</a>
</div>
<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="79">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$gu-nian-zhi-10" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/gu-nian-zhi-10" class="zg-link" title="顾念之">顾念之</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$hang-y-68" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/hang-y-68" class="zg-link" title="HANG Y">HANG Y</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$xiao-bing-sheng" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/xiao-bing-sheng" class="zg-link" title="肖炳生">肖炳生</a></span>
