<div class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="2197596" data-action="/answer/content">

<div class=" zm-editable-content clearfix">我来晚了。<br>看到长者、国母、憨豆、少主、雅人叔还有小李都被答过了，我很痛心。好在还有些可以讲的：<br><br>首先练家子走出来一看就是不一样。<br><noscript><img src="//pic2.zhimg.com/d729c531a7d8e024f26d6583f93ca521_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="510" data-rawheight="352" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="510" data-original="//pic2.zhimg.com/d729c531a7d8e024f26d6583f93ca521_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="510" data-rawheight="352" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="510" data-original="//pic2.zhimg.com/d729c531a7d8e024f26d6583f93ca521_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="//pic2.zhimg.com/d729c531a7d8e024f26d6583f93ca521_b.jpg"><br>如果后面有爆炸，不要回头看。<br><noscript><img src="//pic3.zhimg.com/20ba53970709ec4612d557c8ce18924e_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="440" data-rawheight="274" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="440" data-original="//pic3.zhimg.com/20ba53970709ec4612d557c8ce18924e_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="440" data-rawheight="274" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="440" data-original="//pic3.zhimg.com/20ba53970709ec4612d557c8ce18924e_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="//pic3.zhimg.com/20ba53970709ec4612d557c8ce18924e_b.jpg"><br>当然一般人是没有普京那身功夫的，这时候如果有几个忠实的朋友，可以获得团体增益效果。<br><noscript><img src="//pic4.zhimg.com/83eea0bf7c79528fb955fa7d125bc647_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="680" data-rawheight="510" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="680" data-original="//pic4.zhimg.com/83eea0bf7c79528fb955fa7d125bc647_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="680" data-rawheight="510" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="680" data-original="//pic4.zhimg.com/83eea0bf7c79528fb955fa7d125bc647_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="//pic4.zhimg.com/83eea0bf7c79528fb955fa7d125bc647_b.jpg"><br>樱木的身体素质是百里挑一，但是你看宝强哥走的也很阳光自信嘛。<br><noscript><img src="//pic1.zhimg.com/b164328c677a85c211f83561c3fcddb0_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="390" data-rawheight="555" class="content_image" width="390"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="390" data-rawheight="555" class="content_image lazy" width="390" data-actualsrc="//pic1.zhimg.com/b164328c677a85c211f83561c3fcddb0_b.jpg"><br>不仅青壮年男子可以走出阳光自信的步伐，中老年妇女也可以。<br>赵丽蓉老师告诉我们一句口诀：“<b>探戈探戈就是探戈探戈走，三步一窜两回头，五步一下腰，那个六步一招手，然后你再探戈探戈走</b>”。<br><noscript><img src="//pic4.zhimg.com/4c6ef95530b4ca56abc179acc743a6ab_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="641" data-rawheight="476" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="641" data-original="//pic4.zhimg.com/4c6ef95530b4ca56abc179acc743a6ab_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="641" data-rawheight="476" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="641" data-original="//pic4.zhimg.com/4c6ef95530b4ca56abc179acc743a6ab_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="//pic4.zhimg.com/4c6ef95530b4ca56abc179acc743a6ab_b.jpg"><noscript><img src="//pic2.zhimg.com/0afb688591b23caea7e4a4ca1e03ec49_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="641" data-rawheight="479" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="641" data-original="//pic2.zhimg.com/0afb688591b23caea7e4a4ca1e03ec49_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="641" data-rawheight="479" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="641" data-original="//pic2.zhimg.com/0afb688591b23caea7e4a4ca1e03ec49_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="//pic2.zhimg.com/0afb688591b23caea7e4a4ca1e03ec49_b.jpg"><br>最后，光有口诀还不行，赵老师还给了我们心法。<br><noscript><img src="//pic1.zhimg.com/5111f1d21738188d5c34cde0213b5c10_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="643" data-rawheight="478" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="643" data-original="//pic1.zhimg.com/5111f1d21738188d5c34cde0213b5c10_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="643" data-rawheight="478" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="643" data-original="//pic1.zhimg.com/5111f1d21738188d5c34cde0213b5c10_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="//pic1.zhimg.com/5111f1d21738188d5c34cde0213b5c10_b.jpg">


